data.description: This beautiful, 2 bedroom, 2 bathroom condo has so much to offer! Conveniently located, this home has been extremely well cared for and recently updated. The open floor plan and large windows allow for plenty of natural light. Living area boasts a cozy gas fireplace, newly installed vinyl plank flooring, and opens to a covered balcony with additional storage closet. Primary bedroom is spacious, and features a walk-in closet and private primary bathroom with dual sinks and updated tile shower, tub, toilet, lighting and faucets. Interior has fresh paint, and exterior was painted by the HOA in 2023. All appliances stay, including new refrigerator (2023) and washer/dryer (2019), new carpet in bedrooms, and the furnace, a/c and water heater were all replaced in 2022. This home is truly move-in ready! Unit includes a reserved carport located right below the stairs. Community features an outdoor pool and tennis courts, and the location allows for access to dining, shopping, hiking, biking and transportation!
